             was indicted for <rs id="t17860830-7-off35" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17860830-7-off35" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860830-7-off35" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17860830-7-cd36" type="crimeDate">30th day of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860830-7-off35 t17860830-7-cd36"></join> last, two pair of linen sheets, value 5 s. two pillow biers, value 2 s. sixteen stocks, value 10 s. five neck handkerchiefs, value 5 s. five shirts, value 20 s. two napkins, value 2 s. three handkerchiefs, value 6 s. three pair of silk stockings, value 10 s. two pair of nankeen breeches, value 6 s. two pair of casimere breeches, value 6 s. a pair of silk breeches, value 6 s. two pair of Manchester stuff breeches, value 6 s. a canvass bag, value 6 d. a brush, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17860830-7-victim126" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Plowden
                        <interp inst="t17860830-7-victim126" type="surname" value="Plowden"></interp>
