                  </persName>
            .)</p>
               <p>I know these breeches perfectly well, but they are not marked, I have no doubt of them.</p>
               <p>(The waistcoat and breeches deposed to by 
               <persName id="t17860830-7-person139">
                  Francis
                   Plowden
               <interp inst="t17860830-7-person139" type="surname" value="Plowden"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860830-7-person139" type="given" value="Francis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860830-7-person139" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I have nothing to say but what I did before the Justice, that going out of Mr. Plowden's house at night I discovered a man going towards Queen-street with a large bundle, which then appeared to me to be a black; he threw it down, I came and took it up, and took it to my cousin's, and told him it was a parcel of my clothes, and I would call for it in the morning; I afterwards heard of the robbery, and was in hopes the things<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178608300017"></xptr> would be advertised; I was not sure they were Mr. Plowden's things, but not finding them advertised, I began to dispose of them.</p>
               <p>Mr. Garrow. My Lord, as to character I know there were several people who would have attended, but I told his mother and several more people that it was unnecessary.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have given notice to several persons, and three capital merchants to attend.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17860830-7-verdict37" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17860830-7-verdict37" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17860830-7-punish38" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17860830-7-punish38" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860830-7-defend124 t17860830-7-punish38"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
